title: Richard George (MP)
text:
Richard George (1562 – c. 1613), of <a href="Baunton">Baunton</a>, <a href="Gloucestershire">Gloucestershire</a>, was an English politician.
He was a <a href="Member%20of%20Parliament">Member</a> (MP) of the <a href="Parliament%20of%20England">Parliament of England</a> for <a href="Cirencester%20%28UK%20Parliament%20constituency%29">Cirencester</a> in 1601.
